    "testimonial-slide-1-review": "Fantastic, friendly and personal service. And fantastic product - over the years I've ordered a coffee table, bedside tables, kitchen table and bed - all beautifully crafted products that will last a lifetime and at a decent price. They really care about their customers. Thank you!",
    "testimonial-slide-1-name": "Katie Scotland, Bath",
