    "testimonial-slide-2-review": "From start to finish, our experience of Eat Sleep Live has been great. Personable, responsive and always eager to help. And the bed we ordered is beautiful! We'd have no hesitation in recommending Eat Sleep Live to anyone.",
    "testimonial-slide-2-name": "Stephen Taylor, Glasgow",
    "testimonial-slide-3-image": "shopify://shop_images/avatar-image_bbd03bcb-387d-4652-9631-dc73a532fb93.png",
