    "cart_vendor_enable": false,
    "ajax_cart_method": "drawer",
    "cart_tab_title_1": "LOVINGLY HAND CRAFTED",
    "cart_tab_content_1": "Once your order is placed the journey begins and we will schedule your furniture to be lovingly hand crafted. \r\n\r\nExciting times!",
    "cart_tab_title_2": "KEEP YOU IN THE LOOP",
    "cart_tab_content_2": "We will contact you once we begin crafting your furniture with an update and again in the final stages to discuss suitable delivery dates. \r\n\r\nComing to you soon!",
    "cart_tab_title_3": "PERSONALLY DELIVERED BY US",
    "cart_tab_content_3": "Our expert delivery duo will carefully place your furniture in situ, complete any required assembly and fit protective pads where needed. \r\n\r\nComplimentary wax and aftercare advice supplied with a smile. \r\n\r\nSit back and relax!",
    "cart_tab_title_4": "ALWAYS THERE FOR YOU",
    "cart_tab_content_4": "Now your Eat Sleep Live furniture is part of your family it is ready to begin its new chapter.\r\n\r\nAs a lifelong friend of eat sleep live we will always be there for you.\r\n\r\nLove your furniture!",
    "our-story-section-1-title": "Our Story",
    "our-story-section-1-text": "“Friends are the family you choose.”<br><br>\r\nGreat friends are reliable and loyal. They are unique and we love them. They are always there when we need them.<br><br>\r\n\r\nWe believe furniture shouldn’t be “here today, gone tomorrow”. It\r\nshould be lovingly crafted to last a lifetime.<br><br>\r\n\r\nMuch like a great friend, it becomes part of the family.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThat’s how we view furniture.",
    "our-story-section-2-title": "Founded in 2004",
    "our-story-section-2-text": "Eat Sleep Live was founded in 2004 by Mark Godsell-Fletcher. Driven by a lack of high quality furniture to rival the mass produced alternatives,\r\nMark saw the need for a more personal approach to creating unique furniture that will last a lifetime.",
    "our-story-section-3-title": "Incredible Journey",
    "our-story-section-3-text": "His first design was the Hudson dining table, hand-crafted from solid British reclaimed wood in a timeless design that is still going strong today. Seeing the incredible journey this beautiful wood had been on, a passion to give it a new lease of life was born.",
    "our-story-section-4-title": "Passionate skilled craftsman",
    "our-story-section-4-text": "Eat Sleep Live now has several collections and an enthusiastic team of passionate skilled craftsman who ensure every piece is given the same care and\r\nattention as that very first piece.",
    "our-story-section-5-title": "Get in touch",
    "our-story-section-5-text": "We love to share our passion for furniture, so <a href=\"/pages/get-in-touch\">contact one of our experts</a> for a more personal customer experience.",
    "how-we-work-section-1-title": "Get the ball rolling",
    "how-we-work-section-1-text": "You can order online, pop into our workshop or living showroom or chat over the phone - we are here to help.\n<br><br>\nYour order is then scheduled to be lovingly hand crafted.",
    "how-we-work-section-1-button": "Get in touch",
    "how-we-work-section-1-link": "/pages/get-in-touch",
    "how-we-work-section-2-title": "Personally delivered by us",
    "how-we-work-section-2-text": "We will keep you in the loop and once your unique furniture is complete our own expert 2 man team will deliver and install it carefully in your home.\n<br><br>\nYou sit back and relax.",
    "how-we-work-section-2-button": "Learn more",
    "how-we-work-section-2-link": "/pages/delivery",
    "how-we-work-section-3-title": "Always there for you",
    "how-we-work-section-3-text": "Our friendly delivery duo will give you aftercare information, fit any protective pads where needed and supply complimentary wax. \n<br><br>\nThey will have had a hand in either hand crafting or finishing your furniture so can answer any questions you may have.\n<br><br>\nAfterwards we will make sure you are completely happy and we will always be there if you need us.",
    "how-we-work-section-3-button": "Learn more",
    "how-we-work-section-3-link": "/pages/aftercare",
    "showroom_header": "Showroom",
