    "workshop_opening_hours": "<br>Call 01159 700 060 to book an appointment Monday - Friday.<br><br>",
    "workshop_extra": "",
    "showroom_page_title": "Visit our showroom",
    "showroom_page_description": "<p>Pop in to our Nottingham city centre showroom where Rach, Leah or Mark will be on hand to answer any questions. </p> We’ll get the kettle on!\r\n<p>We have also partnered with like minded companies to showcase the best of British upholstery and lighting. Some of which is exclusive to the showroom.</p>",
    "showroom_page_address": "<p>The Archer Exchange<br>139 Lower Parliament Street<br>Nottingham<br>NG1 1EE</p>\r\n<p>Tel: 01159 700 060</p>",
    "showroom_page_opening_times": "<p><b><u>Opening Hours</u></b></p>\r\n<p>Mon - Thurs: 10am - 6pm<br>Fri - Sat: 10am - 4pm<br>Sunday & Out of Hours: By Appointment</p>\r\n<p><b><u>Parking</u></b></p>\r\n<p>On street parking on <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/kgrWU\" target=\"_blank\">Boston Street</a>, or the <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/qUdlH\" target=\"_blank\">Arena car park</a> nearby.</p>",
    "showroom_page_iframe_code": "<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d600.9223055336474!2d-1.1404495118369449!3d52.95401480669384!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zNTLCsDU3JzE0LjQiTiAxwrAwOCcyMy42Ilc!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1470325257866\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border: 0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>",
    "workshop_page_title": "Visit Us",
    "workshop_page_description": "<p>Visiting us has now resumed so you are very welcome to come and see us and our beautiful furniture.\n<b> It is by appointment only</b> so we can follow social distancing guidelines so get in touch to arrange. </p><b> \n</b>",
    "workshop_page_address": "<p>The Old Joinery Mill<br>2 Nuthall Road<br>Nottingham<br>NG8 5AZ</p>\n<p>Tel: 01159 700 060</p>\n\nCompany reg no. 05263088\n<p>Vat No. 275 8812 62</p>",
    "workshop_page_opening_times": "<p><b><u>Opening Times</u></b></p>\n<p>Monday - Friday:\n 9.00am to 5.00pm<br>Saturday: 9.00am to 1.00pm<br>Weekends & Out Of Hours: by appointment<br> BANK HOLIDAYS: CLOSED FRIDAY 8TH MAY AND MONDAY 25TH MAY! </p><p><b>\n</b></p><p></p><p><b><b><b><u>Parking</u></b></b></b></p><b><b>\n</b></b><p>There is plenty of free parking at the workshop & showrooms.</p>",
    "workshop_page_iframe_code": "<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d600.7196025247372!2d-1.1872865179398306!3d52.968601680979106!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4879c1ede30bd511%3A0x3fd1c544419d35cd!2sEat%20Sleep%20Live!5e0!3m2!1sen!2suk!4v1567158847820!5m2!1sen!2suk\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border: 0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>",
